ADDIS ABABA, Ethiopia, February 21, 2023/APO Group/ --
                                                        
                            The Office of the President has today announced the appointment of Mrs Sarah Romain as the new Chief Executive Officer of the Seychelles Petroleum Company Limited (SEYPEC) effective from the 1st February, 2023.
                                Mrs Romain joined SEYPEC in 2010, as Assistant Commercial Manager and has since held several leadership positions, within the same company
                            



Mrs Romain has 27 years of experience working in both the public and private sector.

Mrs Romain joined SEYPEC in 2010, as Assistant Commercial Manager and has since held several leadership positions, within the same company. Until most recently she was the acting Chief Executive Officer of the SEYPEC.